    <link href="/2022/01/02/GitHub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <url>/2022/01/02/GitHub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-安装必备环境"><a href="#1-安装必备环境" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装必备环境"></a>1. 安装必备环境</h2><ol><li>安装Git和Node.js</li><li>在CMD命令行中输入下面的命令查看是否安装成功</li></ol><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">git --version<br>node -v<br>npm -v<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220165728397.png" alt="image-20211220165728397"></p><h2 id="2-连接GitHub"><a href="#2-连接GitHub" class="headerlink" title="2. 连接GitHub"></a>2. 连接GitHub</h2><ol><li>在Git中进行下面操作，设置用户名和邮箱</li></ol><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">&quot;jiulinger&quot;</span><br>git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2711965146@qq.com&quot;</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>创建SSH秘钥，在Git中进行下面操作</li></ol><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2711965146@qq.com&quot;</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>执行上面操作后，连续点击回车，完成后如下图</li></ol><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220170250138.png" alt="image-20211220170250138"></p><ol start="4"><li>找到生成的秘钥文件，并赋值其中的全部内容</li></ol><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220170704263.png" alt=" "></p><ol start="5"><li>在GitHub的Settings页面内，选择SSH and GPG keys,点击New SSH key,自动以Title后并将刚才复制的秘钥内容复制进key下方的输入框内，最后点击Add SSH key</li></ol><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220171541626.png" alt="image-20211220171541626"></p><ol start="6"><li>验证连接是否成功，在Git中进行下面操作</li></ol><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">ssh git<span class="hljs-meta">@github</span>.com <br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>提示你是否确认时，输入：yes</p><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220172035835.png" alt="image-20211220172035835"></p><h2 id="3-创建GitHub仓库"><a href="#3-创建GitHub仓库" class="headerlink" title="3. 创建GitHub仓库"></a>3. 创建GitHub仓库</h2><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220173333952.png" alt="image-20211220173333952"></p><h2 id="4-在本地安装Hexo博客"><a href="#4-在本地安装Hexo博客" class="headerlink" title="4. 在本地安装Hexo博客"></a>4. 在本地安装Hexo博客</h2><ol><li>在自定义文件夹内打开CMD命令行进行以下操作</li></ol><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">npm install -g hexo-cli<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220175350022.png" alt="image-20211220175350022"></p><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220175403090.png" alt="image-20211220175403090"></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">hexo init Hexo<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220175429424.png" alt="image-20211220175429424"></p><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220175514262.png" alt="image-20211220175514262"></p><ol start="2"><li>执行hexo命令，在本地生成博客页面</li></ol><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">hexo clean  <span class="hljs-comment">//清除缓存文件 (db.json) 和已生成的静态文件 (public)。</span><br>hexo g<span class="hljs-comment">//生成博客网站静态文件。</span><br>hexo d<span class="hljs-comment">//部署网站到GitHub。</span><br>hexo s<span class="hljs-comment">//启动服务器。默认情况下，访问网址为： http://localhost:4000/。</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5-部署Hexo到GitHub"><a href="#5-部署Hexo到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="5. 部署Hexo到GitHub"></a>5. 部署Hexo到GitHub</h2><ol><li>安装Git推送功能</li></ol><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">npm install --save hexo-deployer-git<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>修改配置文件_config.yml</li></ol><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs css">deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repository: git@github.com:jiulinger/jiulinger.github.io.git<br>  branch: master<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>执行下面操作将博客部署到GitHub</li></ol><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">hexo clean <br>hexo g<br>hexo d<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220183707798.png" alt="image-20211220183707798"></p><h2 id="6-自定义Hexo域名"><a href="#6-自定义Hexo域名" class="headerlink" title="6. 自定义Hexo域名"></a>6. 自定义Hexo域名</h2><ol><li>创建CNAME无后缀文件，将域名填写进去</li></ol><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220191232135.png" alt="image-20211220191232135"></p><ol start="2"><li>在GitHub中的Pages页面中将域名添加进去</li></ol><p><img src="https://yp.jiulinger.cn/images/image-20211220191644995.png" alt="image-20211220191644995"></p>]]></content>
    
    
